text: National Ethnographic Museum is the national ethnographic museum of Guinea- Bissau. It is situated in Bissau, and is one of two major museums in the country. As of 1998 it had a library of 14,000 volumes. ==References== Category:Buildings and structures in Bissau Category:Museums in Guinea-Bissau Category:Ethnographic museums Category:National museums
